## 🎯 Essential Test Commands for Operations

### **📋 PRODUCTION-READY TEST EXECUTION:**
```bash
# Complete containerized test suite execution
elixir scripts/testing/comprehensive_containerized_test_executor.exs

# Container-enforced test execution
podman exec intelitor-demo elixir scripts/testing/comprehensive_containerized_test_executor.exs

# Unit tests with coverage in container
